  <article><div class="timeline-marker"><span>06</span><small>Today</small></div><div><h2>The purpose behind Nirog Bhumi</h2><p>Nirog Bhumi carries this journey forward: making natural healing clearer, more accessible and easier to practise at home, while keeping diabetes care measurable, responsible and connected with appropriate medical supervision.</p></div></article>
